Uses of Package
voicesplitting.parsing

  • Packages that use voicesplitting.parsing 
    Package Description
    voicesplitting.gui
    Provides all of the classes used in running the GUI version of the VoiceSplitting project.
    voicesplitting.parsing
    Provides classes which can read and write MIDI files.
    voicesplitting.voice.hmm
    Provides the HMM-based voice splitting model which is the main focus of this project.
  • Classes in voicesplitting.parsing used by voicesplitting.gui 
    Class and Description
    NoteListGenerator
    A NoteListGenerator parses Note On and Note Off events and generates a List of the MidiNotes present in any given song.
  • Classes in voicesplitting.parsing used by voicesplitting.parsing 
    Class and Description
    NoteEventParser
    A NoteEventParser is any class which can handle MIDI Note On and Note Off events.
